    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告 本游戏包含闪烁的灯光，可能会引发光敏性癫痫或其他光敏性疾病患者的癫痫发作。有此类病史的玩家应谨慎操作，并考虑在游戏前咨询医生。建议玩家自行斟酌。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款令人不寒而栗的第一人称恐怖游戏中，你将陷入一片漆黑。为了在阴森恐怖的环境中穿梭，你必须对着麦克风说话，利用声波来创建一个临时的环境视觉呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/8fc645eba6718dfa39653681ba364e48.poster.avif?t=1729242289\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/8fc645eba6718dfa39653681ba364e48.webm?t=1729242289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/8fc645eba6718dfa39653681ba364e48.mp4?t=1729242289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心，一个可怕的怪物潜伏在阴影中，被你的声音所吸引。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/cb6109da6f9165c3bb94c39a4ca20631.poster.avif?t=1729242289\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/cb6109da6f9165c3bb94c39a4ca20631.webm?t=1729242289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205820/extras/cb6109da6f9165c3bb94c39a4ca20631.mp4?t=1729242289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否智胜怪物，逃出这场致命的猫鼠游戏，还是只能在黑暗中尖叫？</p>",
